  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pachinko TD is a physics-based, minimalist tower defense game. Inspired by Thronefall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make simple choices between strengthening your defenses or boosting your economy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/730a4787eeca55c218ed8640a7d1046e.poster.avif?t=1742235139\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/730a4787eeca55c218ed8640a7d1046e.webm?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/730a4787eeca55c218ed8640a7d1046e.mp4?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter a variety of cute but dangerous enemies, each with unique challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/c22d7e24baff0ae6df51c7e7404e4898.poster.avif?t=1742235139\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/c22d7e24baff0ae6df51c7e7404e4898.webm?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/c22d7e24baff0ae6df51c7e7404e4898.mp4?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>Minimalist does not mean easy, so be prepared for a challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/05244b8e0f8e31ca3ffcaed2bb99fd28.poster.avif?t=1742235139\" width=658 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/05244b8e0f8e31ca3ffcaed2bb99fd28.webm?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/05244b8e0f8e31ca3ffcaed2bb99fd28.mp4?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features 20 levels that provide 10+ hours of core gameplay and an Endless mode. Try the free demo!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pachinko TD is a physics-based, minimalist tower defense game. Inspired by Thronefall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make simple choices between strengthening your defenses or boosting your economy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/730a4787eeca55c218ed8640a7d1046e.poster.avif?t=1742235139\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/730a4787eeca55c218ed8640a7d1046e.webm?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/730a4787eeca55c218ed8640a7d1046e.mp4?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter a variety of cute but dangerous enemies, each with unique challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/c22d7e24baff0ae6df51c7e7404e4898.poster.avif?t=1742235139\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/c22d7e24baff0ae6df51c7e7404e4898.webm?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/c22d7e24baff0ae6df51c7e7404e4898.mp4?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>Minimalist does not mean easy, so be prepared for a challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/05244b8e0f8e31ca3ffcaed2bb99fd28.poster.avif?t=1742235139\" width=658 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/05244b8e0f8e31ca3ffcaed2bb99fd28.webm?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374070/extras/05244b8e0f8e31ca3ffcaed2bb99fd28.mp4?t=1742235139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features 20 levels that provide 10+ hours of core gameplay and an Endless mode. Try the free demo!</p>",
